{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I hear-- this is always the thing that I was always looking for-- somebody talking in an Austrian dialect.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I see these guys sitting down there with guns, and bedraggled, and tired, soldiers coming from somewhere in the front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know where the hell they came from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I hear-- I hear one guy saying-- he was definitely from Vienna-- he looked at us, he said, those are Judenschwein.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "These are-- these are, uh, uh, jew pigs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I nearly-- I nearly said to him, yeah, it'll be over for you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'll tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It wasn't funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was really bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we landed in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And Dachau was in an uproar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was, uh, it wasn't run like a camp anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Hunger.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were-- oh boy, were we hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I'll tell you, we were so hungry, it wasn't funny.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And to, uh-- [SIGHS] there are many-- there are so many stories that I can tell, but I know you can't do them all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the-- the thing is that, in Dahau, it was a Sunday-- that I know-- and I didn't-- we didn't have any bread for two days.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, uh, in Dachau, there was-- there was real-- there's not very much to tell about Dachau as such, because we didn't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't there too long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were, we were-- we were-- I mean, you know, this was the first time that-- when you were in Auschwitz, you had three meals-- so-called meals-- a day.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had tea in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had soup at lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
